I'm currently a college student, and for my final class for my Associate's degree, I decided to make a mobile game. While working on publishing it on the Google Play Store, I found out that officially publishing it in such a way would require a Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, both of which the Play Store recommends I consult my legal advisor for (scary!). But then I stumbled across your privacy policy generator, and it is incredibly easy to use and absolutely a life-saver! Thank you for making such a straightforward tool! And especially being able to generate it as html made it perfect to use.
